Package guardians.controllers.exceptions

Contains the exceptions that will be thrown when handling a request

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AllowedShiftNotFoundException
    This class represents the exception that will be thrown whenever a requested AllowedShift is not found
    AlreadyExistsException
    All exceptions that represent an Entity has been tried to be newly created but already existed will extend this one
    CalendarAlreadyExistsException
    This exception will be thown whenever a Calendar is to be created, but it already exists
    CalendarNotFoundException
    This exception will be thrown whenever a requested Calendar is not found in the database
    DoctorAlreadyExistsException
    This exception will be thrown whenever a new Doctor is to be created, but it already exists in the database
    DoctorDeletedException
    This exception will be thrown whenever a Doctor is going to be edited, but it is in the DELETED status
    DoctorNotFoundException
    This class represents the exception that will be thrown when a requested Doctor is not found.
    InvalidAbsenceException
    This class represents the exception to be thrown when an Absence is not valid
    InvalidDayConfigurationException
    This exception will be thrown whenever a DayConfiguration violates one or more constraint
    InvalidEntityException
    All exceptions that represent an Entity is not valid will extend this one
    InvalidScheduleStatusException
    This exception will be thrown when a Schedule.ScheduleStatus is to be created from a String, and the status does not exist
    InvalidScheduleStatusTransitionException
    This exception will be thrown when a Schedule is to be transitions from one state to another, but the transition is not valid
    NotFoundException
    All exceptions that represent a resource has not been found will extend this one
    ScheduleAlreadyExistsException
    This exception will be thrown whenever a Schedule is to be generated, but it already exists
    ScheduleNotFoundException
    This class represents the exception that will be thrown whenever the Calendar related to a Schedule is not found in the database.
    ShiftConfigurationAlreadyExistsException
    This exception will be thrown whenever a new ShiftConfiguration for a Doctor is to be created, but this Doctor already has one
    ShiftConfigurationNotFoundException
    This class represents the exception that will be thrown when a requested ShiftConfiguration is not found.

Package guardians.controllers.exceptions Description
